The paper discusses improving the generalization ability of deep convolutional neural networks (DCNN) through a modification of the softmax function. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on DCNNs and image classification tasks, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
